{
  "id": "5c7fa97d343d680017e0e2f6",
  "title": "マクレランドの欲求理論",
  "created": 1551870374,
  "updated": 1646364634,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c7fa97d343d680017e0e2f6",
      "text": "マクレランドの欲求理論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870374,
      "updated": 1551870374
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fa9a5aff09e00000425f1",
      "text": "\t[マクレランド]が提唱した[モチベーション理論]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870374,
      "updated": 1551870392
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fa9b5aff09e00000425f3",
      "text": "\t[達成欲求]、[権力欲求]、[親和欲求]の3つがある、という理論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870390,
      "updated": 1551870457
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fa9a5aff09e00000425f2",
      "text": "\t のちに[回避欲求]が追加されて[4つの欲求]になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870374,
      "updated": 1615561499
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fa9deaff09e00000425f4",
      "text": "　西尾的にはこの「[達成欲求]、[権力欲求]、[親和欲求]、[回避欲求]」の4つで考える方法がとても有益に感じる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870430,
      "updated": 1608473026
    },
    {
      "id": "5fdf59c2aff09e00004d0314",
      "text": "　　[マズローの欲求段階説]も人間の欲求をいくつかに分類した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1608473026,
      "updated": 1608473273
    },
    {
      "id": "5fdf5ad3aff09e00004d0318",
      "text": "　　　それが階層になっていると考えた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1608473300,
      "updated": 1608473311
    },
    {
      "id": "5fdf5ab8aff09e00004d0316",
      "text": "　　　これは暗黙に「人間はみな同じ欲求階層を持っている」と仮定している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1608473273,
      "updated": 1608473332
    },
    {
      "id": "5fdf5af7aff09e00004d0319",
      "text": "　　　また、表出している欲求が異なる人を見た時に「欲求の達成度合いの高い人/低い人がいる」と人に上下をつける解釈になってしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1608473335,
      "updated": 1608473390
    },
    {
      "id": "5fdf5b2eaff09e00004d031a",
      "text": "　　翻ってマクレランドの方は4つの欲求に上下関係はない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1608473390,
      "updated": 1608473417
    },
    {
      "id": "5fdf5b4aaff09e00004d031b",
      "text": "　　　人によって欲求に[多様性]があることが自然に表現されている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1608473418,
      "updated": 1608474246
    },
    {
      "id": "5fdf59acaff09e00004d0313",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1608473004,
      "updated": 1608473004
    },
    {
      "id": "5fdf59a0aff09e00004d0312",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1608472992,
      "updated": 1608472992
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fa9faaff09e00000425f5",
      "text": "\t達成欲求",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870458,
      "updated": 1551870634
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7faaa9aff09e00000425f7",
      "text": "\t\t[成し遂げたい]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870634,
      "updated": 1551872671
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7faab2aff09e00000425f8",
      "text": "\t\t[効率]的にやりたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870643,
      "updated": 1551872674
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fab06aff09e00000425fa",
      "text": "\t\t後にマクレランドは[コンピテンシー理論]を生み出す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870727,
      "updated": 1551870753
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7faadcaff09e00000425f9",
      "text": " 権力欲求",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870684,
      "updated": 1551870786
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fab3daff09e00000425fb",
      "text": "\t\t他者に[影響力]を行使したい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870781,
      "updated": 1551872662
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fab4daff09e00000425fd",
      "text": "\t\t[コントロール]したい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870798,
      "updated": 1551872664
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fab51aff09e00000425fe",
      "text": " 親和欲求",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870801,
      "updated": 1551870866
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fab75aff09e00000425ff",
      "text": "\t\t他者との[交友関係]を作りたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870838,
      "updated": 1551872679
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fab9faff09e0000042603",
      "text": "\t\t他者から[好かれたい]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870879,
      "updated": 1551872681
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7faba7aff09e0000042605",
      "text": "\t回避欲求",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870888,
      "updated": 1551870911
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fabbeaff09e0000042606",
      "text": "\t\t[失敗したくない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870911,
      "updated": 1551872684
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7fabd6aff09e0000042607",
      "text": "\t\t[ストレス]を避けたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870935,
      "updated": 1551872686
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7faba7aff09e0000042604",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551870888,
      "updated": 1551870888
    },
    {
      "id": "622187d8aff09e0000cfc2c2",
      "text": "[デービッド・マクレランド]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646364633,
      "updated": 1646364634
    },
